    <string name="dialog_title_help">Help &amp; Tips</string>
    <string name="help_message"><![CDATA[
• Text can be shared from other apps directly here (Share button in that app).

• Select text in any app and choose "Smart Text Reader" from the menu - it reads exactly what you selected.

• The Image button recognizes text from a photo or screenshot, it also works offline.

• The Link button downloads and reads text from a web page. It usually doesn\'t work for Facebook and Instagram due to technical limitations of those platforms - select the text directly in the app instead.

• Tapping anywhere in the text starts reading from exactly that position.

• In Settings you can change the voice, reading volume, and speed.
]]></string>
